ActSecurity of Information Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the Security of Information Act
PrecisOrder amending the SCHEDULE TO THE SECURITY OF INFORMATION ACT in order to (1) protect Canada's national security interests and the Government's most operationally sensitive information; and (2) provide additional assurances to Canada's international partners and allies that speciall operational information shared with Canada will be protected.
